OL,6,FA court has heard how three women who
OL,7,Fcovered up for the man accused of
OL,8,Fmurdering Co Armagh show-jumper Katie
OL,9,FSimpson were complicit in a conspiracy
OL,10,Fof silence.
OL,12,FA defence barrister told the Judge
OL,13,Fthat Jonathan Creswell had 'unfettered
OL,14,Fcontrol' over the lives of so many
OL,15,Fyoung women.
