OL,3,C'Conspiracy of silence' over Katie
OL,4,CSimpson death
OL,6,FThe 36-year-old was found dead at home
OL,7,Fin Londonderry back in April, the day
OL,8,Fafter his trial started for the rape
OL,9,Fand murder of his ex-partner's sister
OL,10,FKatie Simpson in Lettershandoney in
OL,11,FAugust 2020.
OL,13,FThe prosecution claimed Creswell
OL,14,Fstrangled Katie out of jealousy and
OL,15,Fthen tried to make it look like
OL,16,Fsuicide.
