OL,3,C'Conspiracy of silence' over Katie
OL,4,CSimpson death
OL,6,FThe 21-year-old talented show-jumper
OL,7,Fwas rushed to Altnagelvin Hospital
OL,8,Fwere she spent a number of days on
OL,9,Flife support but sadly died on 9
OL,10,FAugust.
OL,12,FOn Friday, during a sentence hearing,
OL,13,FLondonderry Crown Court heard how 30-
OL,14,Fyear-old Hayley Robb, of Weavers
OL,15,FMeadow in Banbridge, was in a sexual
OL,16,Frelationship with Jonathan Creswell
OL,17,Fand how she cleaned up Katie's blood,
OL,18,Fand washed Creswell's clothes after
OL,19,Fgetting dragged into it and being told
OL,20,Fnot to breathe a word.
