OL,3,C'Conspiracy of silence' over Katie
OL,4,CSimpson death
OL,6,FThe court was also told how Rose De
OL,7,FMontmorency-Wright, who at one point
OL,8,Flived with Creswell, admitted
OL,9,Fwithholding information.
OL,11,FThe prosecution said the 23-year-old
OL,12,Fof Craigantlet Road in Newtownards,
OL,13,Ftold police Creswell was a friend,
OL,14,Fsomeone she looked up to, and she
OL,15,Fwanted to 'have Jonny's back'.
OL,17,FAnd the court heard how 42-year-old
OL,18,FJill Robinson, of Black Fort Road in
OL,19,FOmagh, had previously been in a
OL,20,Frelationship with Jonathan Creswell
OL,21,Fand she helped wash his clothes.
