OL,6,FKatie's family, including her mother
OL,7,Fand sister Christina, who was
OL,8,FCreswell's partner at the time of her
OL,9,Fdeath, were all in court on Friday.
OL,11,FThe Judge said he has a lot to
OL,12,Fconsider and would sentence all three
OL,13,Fon 14 June.
